				<h3>Re: Transmission built in.</h3>
				<div class="date"><img src="./styles/absolution/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" />Posted: <strong>Mon May 02, 2011 4:37 pm</strong></div>
				<div class="author">by <strong>J.M.</strong></div>
				<div class="content">Edit /etc/features.conf and change &quot;supportsTransmission&quot; = 0 to &quot;supportsTransmission&quot; = 1<br /><br />Then open the goflex home web page, go to preferences and activate the torrent files.</div>
			</div>
